These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
House: art-deco, craftsman, futuristic
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, surfing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
2. the futuristic house is the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the art-deco house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| House   | art-deco | craftsman | futuristic   |
| Sport      | biathlon    | rugby  | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
3 different pets are kept: fish, turtle, snake
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, nigerian
1. the argentine is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
2. the canadian is on the far left##1
3. the canadian is the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Pet      | turtle | fish     | snake      |
| Nationality   | canadian | argentine | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, tea, water
The people have 3 different jobs:  teacher, doctor, videographer
1. the person drinking tea is on the right of the doctor##1
2. the person drinking water is on the left of the videographer##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | water  | tea       |
| Job       | teacher     | doctor | videographer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, radish, zucchini
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, zinnia, poppy
1. the person eating radish is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | zucchini    | radish     | pomegranate |
| Flower   | poppy | dahlia | zinnia     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, hedgehog
3 different games are played: chess, bridge, domino
1. the person playing bridge is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person playing chess##1
4. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | bird     | hedgehog |
| Game   | domino        | chess | bridge    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, plum, strawberry
3 different pets are kept: bird, pony, turtle
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
3. the person eating strawberry is the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | strawberry | kiwi      | plum  |
| Pet   | bird       | pony | turtle |

