.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, animation, sports
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goldfish
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports      | western     | animation    |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goldfish | ferret |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
City: venice, boston, edinburgh
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, card-games, skydiving
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person traveling to boston is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| City    | edinburgh | venice | boston      |
| Hobby   | camping     | skydiving | card-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, game, oliveros
3 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit, rat
1. the owner of the horse is the game-smoker##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
3. the game-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Cigar   | oliveros | game | davidoff  |
| Pet     | rat     | horse      | rabbit |

