.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, tea
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, mouse, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | cola   | sprite    | tea    |
| Pet   | mouse | rabbit | hedgehog |

