.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, trance
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, october, december
1. the fan of trance is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | trance   | punk  |
| Birthday   | december    | february | october |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, reggae, salsa
There 3 different types of food: lime, asparagus, zucchini
1. the fan of metal is in the middle##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person eating lime##1
3. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | metal     | reggae   |
| Food   | asparagus | lime | zucchini |

