.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, electrician, security-guard
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, tram
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the security-guard##1
2. the security-guard is on the left of the electrician##1
3. the electrician is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Job   | coach    | security-guard | electrician |
| Transport   | tram | bike     | quad-bike        |

