.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, thriller
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, funk, pop
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Movie-Genre      | adventure  | thriller | disaster  |
| Music-Genre   | funk | pop   | classical |

