.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-17::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, parkour, soccer
There are 3 different nationalities: american, colombian, turkish
1. the turkish is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
3. the american is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |
| Sport           | parkour | soccer | surfing |
| Nationality   | turkish  | american      | colombian |

