.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-19::.
House: modern, gothic-revival, victorian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, house, pop
1. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of pop##1
2. the gothic-revival house is the fan of pop##1
3. the victorian house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| House         | modern | gothic-revival | victorian |
| Music-Genre   | country | pop     | house  |

